Description: egor aids with the process of importing, analyzing
    and visualizing ego-centric network data. It supports several data formats,
    including the export formats of EgoNet (McCarty 2011), EgoWeb 2.0 (Kennedy
    et al.) and openeddi (Eddens/ Fagan). egor offers an interactive (shiny) app
    for the intuitive visualization of ego-centered  networks. It also includes
    procedures for creating and visualizing Clustered Graphs (Lerner et. al
    2008).
